If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, You can contact us:
Address: Dynamic Games LTD, 4 Gershon Shatz St., Tel Aviv 6701738 Israel
By email:
privacy@dynamicgames.net
By visiting this page on our website:
https://support.dynamicgames.net/portal/newticket
