Privacy Center
At Constant Contact, we care deeply about protecting the personal information of our customers, our customers’ contacts, and our website visitors. Security and privacy are at the core of our business practices and product offerings.  Our goal is to be as transparent and forthright as possible about our privacy practices.  For more information, please refer to the following links:
Privacy Notice
