Customer Contact Data Notice
Our Customer Contact Data Notice describes how we use our customers’ contact data. We are a service provider to our customers and only send communications to a customer’s contacts at the customer’s direction.
SafeUnsubscribe
®
If you no longer wish to receive emails from one of our customers, every email includes a SafeUnsubscribe® link assuring your customers that you have used a legitimate permission-based email provider.
